profile: A 29 year old person, living in a family_single family with 3_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 53672 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income>=30000 AND p.income<60000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Eat'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>=50 AND p.age<60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Eat'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
amenity_recommendation: [{'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Full-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.44}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Limited-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.27}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Snack and Nonalcoholic Beverage Bars', 'score': 0.2}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Drinking Places', 'score': 0.03}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Special Food Services', 'score': 0.02}]

        WHERE (p.age>=40 AND p.age<50) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Eat'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
amenity_recommendation: [{'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Full-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.44}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Limited-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.28}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Snack and Nonalcoholic Beverage Bars', 'score': 0.18}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Drinking Places', 'score': 0.08}]

profile: A 70 year old person, living in a married_couple family with 7_plus_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 6666 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Eat'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
amenity_recommendation: [{'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Full-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.45}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Snack and Nonalcoholic Beverage Bars', 'score': 0.23}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Limited-Service Restaurants', 'score': 0.18}, {'choice': 'F&B Eatery/Drinking Places', 'score': 0.12}]
amenity_final_choice: F&B Eatery/Snack and Nonalcoholic Beverage Bars

        WHERE (p.age>=30 AND p.age<40) OR (p.income>=90000 AND p.income<120000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Eat'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
